print('internal', R)
Rext = np.sqrt(9.81 * 2000)/1e-4
print('external', Rext)
print('speed', np.sqrt(gp*h))
l = np.pi * 2

f=1e-4
k = np.sqrt((om**2 - f**2)/gp/h)
print(2*np.pi / k)

ommax = beta * R / 2
print('Min T [h]', 2*np.pi/ommax/3600)

print('Min TBT [h]', 2*np.pi/ommaxBT/3600)
